```agda
data Nat : Set where
  zero : Nat
  suc  : Nat -> Nat

square : Nat -> Nat
square zero = zero
square (suc n) = suc (suc (square n))

sumOfSquares : Nat -> Nat -> Nat
sumOfSquares a b = square a + square b

squareOfSum : Nat -> Nat -> Nat
squareOfSum a b = square (suc (suc a + suc (suc b)))

check : (a : Nat) -> (b : Nat) -> sumOfSquares a b ≡ squareOfSum a b
check zero _ = refl
check (suc a) zero = refl
check (suc a) (suc b) = cong suc (check a b)
```
